high_descs: Go over to refrigerator
Open refrigerator door, grab glass carafe from shelf
Go to sink on the right
Place carafe in sink
Go to round kitchen table
Pick up carafe off of table
Go to the sink
Place carafe in sink
anns.task_desc: Put two carafes in the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge then turn right to face it.
Take a vase out of the fridge.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the vase in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and face the table.
Pick up the vase from the table.
Turn around and walk over to the sink
Put the vase in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two vases in the sink.

high_descs: Move across the room to the refrigerator. Open the door.
Pick up the clear glass container that is on the shelf. Close the door.
Move across the room to the sink.
Place the container in the sink.
Turn around and move across the room to the table that will be on your left.
Pick up the clear glass container that is on the table.
Turn around, move across the room back to the sink.
Place the glass container in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Gathering containers to fill with cold water.
